本库\\n- 更新索引\\n\\n### 2.4 评分与输出 (1分钟)\\n- 按自我评估模板打分\\n- 记录到 self-evolution-system.md\\n- **输出报告到飞书，包含进化次数**\\n\\n## 产出标准（必须达到）\\n- 笔记 ≥1 篇\\n- 价值分 ≥3 分\\n- 知识应用 ≥1 项\\n- 版本记录 ≥1 次\\n\\n## 报告格式（必须包含）\\n# 🛡️ 管管进化报告 - 第[N]次进化\\n\\n| 指标 | 数值 |\\n|------|------|\\n| 进化次数 | N |\\n| 价值分 | X |\\n| 笔记 | X 篇 |\\n| 模板 | X 个 |\\n| 案例 | X 个 |\\n\\n开始！\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 900\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"to\": \"oc_887bdef216b66d0eb1934e2bb90758cf\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1773850800000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1773848400004,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 256903,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"lastDelivered\": true,\n        \"runningAtMs\": 1773850523563\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"total\": 3,\n  \"offset\": 0,\n  \"limit\": 3,\n  \"hasMore\": false,\n  \"nextOffset\": null\n}"}],"details":{"jobs":[{"id":"58b564ba-7837-434a-9d8e-632542b6443d","agentId":"xiao-yi","sessionKey":"agent:xiao-yi:main","name":"小艺进化心跳 - 每15分钟","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1773837490104,"updatedAtMs":1773848732793,"schedule":{"expr":"*/15 * * * *","kind":"cron","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"请执行 perception.py 脚本并输出感知报告。\n\n脚本路径: C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\xiao-yi\\workspace\\perception.py\n\n⚡ 极速模式：直接执行，简洁输出","timeoutSeconds":90},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"feishu","to":"oc_887bdef216b66d0eb1934e2bb90758cf"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1773850500000,"lastRunAtMs":1773848700011,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":32782,"lastDeliveryStatus":"delivered","consecutiveErrors":0,"lastDelivered":true}},{"id":"98eb989c-2294-4d42-b9f4-0c5b17631bfa","agentId":"main","sessionKey":"agent:main:main","name":"Guan-guan Heartbeat - Every 10min","enabled":tr